The '''Irugian Rain Forest''' was a [[Forest/Legends|forest]] on [[Abbaji (Spar sector)|Abbaji]]. It contained one small grove of [[firethorn tree]]s, the only such place in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] where they grew.

